---
title: DepthFusion Retrieval Pipeline (v0.4.0)
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant CC as Claude Code
    participant Hook as SessionStart Hook
    participant MCP as MCP Server
    participant Graph as Knowledge Graph
    participant BM25 as BM25 Engine
    participant Vec as ChromaDB (Tier 2)
    participant RRF as RRF Fusion
    participant Haiku as Haiku Reranker
    participant Store as Discovery Files

    Note over CC,Store: Session Start — Context Injection
    CC->>Hook: new session started
    Hook->>Hook: git log --oneline -5<br/>git branch --show-current<br/>cat BACKLOG.md | head -20
    Hook->>MCP: depthfusion_recall_relevant(auto_query)
    MCP->>Graph: expand_query(terms)
    Graph-->>MCP: expanded_terms[]

    alt Local Mode
        MCP->>BM25: search(expanded_terms, top_k=5)
        BM25-->>MCP: ranked_blocks[]
    end

    alt VPS Tier 1
        MCP->>BM25: search(expanded_terms, top_k=10)
        BM25-->>MCP: ranked_blocks[]
        MCP->>Haiku: rerank(blocks, query)
        Haiku-->>MCP: reranked_blocks[]
    end

    alt VPS Tier 2
        MCP->>BM25: search(expanded_terms, top_k=10)
        MCP->>Vec: search(expanded_terms, top_k=20)
        BM25-->>RRF: bm25_results[]
        Vec-->>RRF: vector_results[]
        RRF->>Haiku: fused_blocks[]
        Haiku-->>MCP: reranked_blocks[]
    end

    MCP->>Graph: boost_scores(results, query_entities)
    Graph-->>MCP: boosted_results[]
    MCP-->>CC: injected context (top-k blocks)

    Note over CC,Store: Session End — Knowledge Capture
    CC->>Hook: PostCompact triggered
    Hook->>MCP: depthfusion_compress_session(tmp_file)
    MCP->>MCP: extract key facts (heuristic/haiku)
    MCP->>Store: write discovery file
    MCP->>Graph: extract_entities(discovery)
    Graph->>Graph: link_edges(new_entities)
    Graph->>Graph: update_store()
